data.description: Back on the market pending release...Call this beauty home just in time for the holidays!  This home boasts 3 levels, 3 bedrooms, and 4 bathrooms providing ample space for both relaxation and entertaining.  Enjoy the eat-in kitchen complete with modern appliances and sliding doors that lead to the deck – a perfect setting for outdoor dining or hosting gatherings with friends and family. The fully finished basement is bathed in natural sunlight, creating a warm and inviting atmosphere throughout.   Conveniently located near several shopping and dining options, this home offers a lifestyle of comfort and convenience. Don't miss the chance to make this your home sweet home – schedule a showing today, as this gem won't last long!
